{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I got a visit almost exactly a year ago,"},{"time":4000,"text":"a little over a year ago, from a very senior person at the Department of Defense."},{"time":8000,"text":"Came to see me and said, \"1,600 of the kids that we've sent out"},{"time":13000,"text":"have come back missing at least one full arm."},{"time":18000,"text":"Whole arm. Shoulder disarticulation."},{"time":21000,"text":"And we're doing the same thing we did for -- more or less,"},{"time":24000,"text":"that we've done since the Civil War, a stick and a hook."},{"time":27000,"text":"And they deserve more than that.\""},{"time":31000,"text":"And literally, this guy sat in my office in New Hampshire and said,"},{"time":35000,"text":"\"I want you to give me something that we can put on these kids"},{"time":38000,"text":"that'll pick up a raisin or a grape off a table,"},{"time":43000,"text":"they'll be able to put it in their mouth without destroying either one,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and they'll be able to know the difference without looking at it.\""},{"time":50000,"text":"You know, had efferent, afferent, and haptic response."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"He finishes explaining that, and I'm waiting for the big 300 pound paper proposal,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and he said, \"That's what I want from you.\""},{"time":63000,"text":"I said, \"Look, you're nuts. That technology's just not available right now."},{"time":70000,"text":"And it can't be done."},{"time":72000,"text":"Not in an envelope of a human arm,"},{"time":75000,"text":"with 21 degrees of freedom, from your shoulder to your fingertips.\""},{"time":80000,"text":"He said, \"About two dozen of these 1,600 kids have come back bilateral."},{"time":88000,"text":"You think it's bad to lose one arm?"},{"time":89000,"text":"That's an inconvenience compared to having both of them gone.\""},{"time":97000,"text":"I got a day job,"},{"time":99000,"text":"and my nights and weekends are already filled up with things like,"},{"time":101000,"text":"let's supply water to the world, and power to the world, and educate all the kids,"},{"time":106000,"text":"which, Chris, I will not talk about. I don't need another mission."}]},{"cues":[{"time":114000,"text":"I keep thinking about these kids with no arms."},{"time":118000,"text":"He says to me, \"We've done some work around the country."},{"time":121000,"text":"We've got some pretty amazing neurology and other people.\""},{"time":125000,"text":"I said, \"I'll take a field trip, I'll go see what you got.\""},{"time":129000,"text":"Over the next month I visited lots of places, some out here, around the country,"},{"time":132000,"text":"found the best of the best."},{"time":134000,"text":"I went down to Washington. I saw these guys, and said,"},{"time":137000,"text":"\"I did what you asked me. I looked at what's out there."},{"time":140000,"text":"I still think you're nuts. But not as nuts as I thought.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":145000,"text":"I put a team together, a little over 13 months ago,"},{"time":149000,"text":"got up to 20 some-odd people."},{"time":152000,"text":"We said, we're going to build a device that does what he wants."},{"time":155000,"text":"We have 14 out of the 21 degrees of freedom;"},{"time":158000,"text":"you don't need the ones in the last two fingers."},{"time":160000,"text":"We put this thing together."},{"time":162000,"text":"A couple of weeks ago we took it down to Walter Reed,"},{"time":165000,"text":"which is unfortunately more in the news these days."},{"time":167000,"text":"We showed it to a bunch of guys."},{"time":169000,"text":"One guy who described himself as being lucky,"},{"time":171000,"text":"because he lost his left arm, and he's a righty."},{"time":177000,"text":"He sat at a table with seven or eight of these other guys."},{"time":179000,"text":"Said he was lucky, because he had his good arm,"},{"time":182000,"text":"and then he pushed himself back from the table. He had no legs."},{"time":186000,"text":"These kids have attitudes that you just can't believe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189000,"text":"So I'm going to show you now, without the skin on it,"},{"time":191000,"text":"a 30-second piece, and then I'm done."},{"time":194000,"text":"But understand what you're looking at"},{"time":197000,"text":"we made small enough to fit on a 50th percentile female,"},{"time":201000,"text":"so that we could put it in any of these people."},{"time":205000,"text":"It's going to go inside something that we use in CAT scans and"},{"time":208000,"text":"MRIs of whatever is their good arm,"},{"time":210000,"text":"to make silicon rubber, then coat it, and paint it in 3D --"},{"time":216000,"text":"exact mirror image of their other limb."},{"time":219000,"text":"So, you won't see all the really cool stuff that's in this series elastic set of 14 actuators,"},{"time":224000,"text":"each one which has its own capability to sense temperature and pressure."},{"time":228000,"text":"It also has a pneumatic cuff that holds it on,"},{"time":230000,"text":"so the more they put themselves under load, the more it attaches."},{"time":234000,"text":"They take the load off, and it becomes, again, compliant."},{"time":237000,"text":"I'm going to show you a guy doing a couple of simple things with this"},{"time":241000,"text":"that we demonstrated in Washington. Can we look at this thing?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Watch the fingers grab. The thumb comes up. Wrist."},{"time":257000,"text":"This weighs 6.9 pounds."},{"time":260000,"text":"Going to scratch his nose."},{"time":265000,"text":"It's got 14 active degrees of freedom."},{"time":267000,"text":"Now he's going to pick up a pen with his opposed thumb and index finger."},{"time":273000,"text":"Now he's going to put that down, pick up a piece of paper,"},{"time":276000,"text":"rotate all the degrees of freedom in his hand and wrist, and read it."},{"time":285000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}